Program: The Documentary
Title: Venezuela - A Week In The Life Of A Country In Chaos
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csvp5r
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Aug 2017
Venezuela has some of the largest oil reserves in the world but incredibly, around four in five Venezuelans live in poverty. The BBC's South America correspondent, Katy Watson, went to cover the unfolding political and economic crisis in Venezuela and found a country divided. (Photo: Anti-government graffiit. Credit: Katy Watson/BBC) Show less